@startuml
autonumber
actor "CRM Collaborator" as Actor
participant ":System" as System

activate Actor
Actor -> System : Initiates Create Show Proposal
activate System
System --> Actor : Lists existing show requests and available resources
Actor -> System : Selects a show request and enters proposal details\n(date, place, duration, number of drones, insurance)
System --> Actor : Confirms successful creation of the show proposal
deactivate System
deactivate Actor

@enduml
